  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Toast the slices of bread until lightly golden.",
    "In a small bowl, mix coconut milk with lime juice and add in ginger powder and turmeric powder. Mix well.",
    "Sprinkle nutritional yeast over the toasted bread slices.",
    "Drizzle the coconut-milk mixture evenly on top of each slice of toast.",
    "Bake for 10 minutes or until heated through and topping is golden brown.",
    "Serve immediately."
